    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普关税临近，世界各国准备应对股市溢出效应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/as-trump-tariffs-near-world-braces-for-stock-market-spillover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普计划于周六对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收 25% 的关税。现在的问题是，这将如何影响全球股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/as-trump-tariffs-near-world-braces-for-stock-market-spillover</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 17:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行机构将于 3 月 6 日就监管事宜征求公众意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/us-bank-agencies-to-seek-public-input-on-regulations-on-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高银行监管机构将于 3 月 6 日举行一次虚拟会议，征求公众对其监管对华尔街公司、消费者和储户的有效性的反馈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/us-bank-agencies-to-seek-public-input-on-regulations-on-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:08:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
