    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙开始使用“美国湾”来向特朗普致敬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令美国重新命名该水域后，雪佛龙公司开始使用“美国湾”而不是“墨西哥湾”来描述其部分最大石油业务所在地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待特朗普对加拿大石油关税的决定，油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普决定对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，油价出现波动，但交易员们仍在猜测原油是否会被免征关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 23:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示，DeepSeek 几乎不会对七大股票造成影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/deepseek-will-hardly-dent-magnificent-seven-stocks-mliv-pulse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，DeepSeek 的出现震动了市场，但彭博市场实时脉搏的最新调查显示，投资者认为这家中国人工智能初创公司对七侠荡寇志的表现造成的影响有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/deepseek-will-hardly-dent-magnificent-seven-stocks-mliv-pulse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 23:28:59 GMT</pubDate>
